Lawatan Delegasi Universitas Subang, Bandung, Indonesia
=======================================================

by [webmaster](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/author/sazizul/ "Posts by webmaster")
 | Mar 13, 2019 | [Global Outreach Program](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/global-outreach-program/)
, [News](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/news/)
, [photo](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/photo/)

![](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/53785454_2377354585643267_8891745422813429760_o-1080x675.jpg)

Fakultas Teknik Universitas Subang, Bandung Indonesia telah datang untuk membuat lawatan ke Fakulti Alam Bina dan Ukur (FABU) pada 12 Mac 2019 yang lepas. Antara tempat yang dilawat ialah Pusat Kajian Alam Bina (KALAM) , FABU.

[More photos (Click here)](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/photos/2019/03/lawatan-delegasi-universitas-subang-bandung-indonesia/)
